<h1>Loader</h1>
<p>Used for communicating a delay in processing.</p>
<h2 id="demo">Demo</h2>
<code-sample>
<m-loader loading>Searching...</m-loader>
<a href="/search"><m-loader>Try again</m-loader></a>
</code-sample>
